    "bio_summary": "Dina Ögon is a music group from Stockholm, Sweden, known for their blend of pop, psychedelic rock, jazz, and soul. The band, formed in 2020, consists of Anna Ahnlund (vocals, guitar), Daniel Ögren (guitar), Christopher Cantillo (drums), and Love Örsan (bass). They describe their music as \"a love child between Fleetwood Mac, Khruangbin, and obscure Motown B-sides.\" Dina Ögon's music is characterized by a playful nostalgia, drawing influences from <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Dina+%C3%96gon\"",
